					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2572203#post-3123088</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2572203/scp-3602#post-3123088</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2017 08:33:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MrWrong</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2039383</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I doubt the GOC can do meaningful feats to kill off the -A instances.</p> <p>In <em>Journey to the West</em>, those monkeys are literally not in the record of deaths. Thus, the problem is that they are not slated to die. To kill them, those monkeys' names have to be re-registered in the record of deaths.</p> <p>And to do that, they have to find the Chinese hell and claim the register from the Kings of Yama and all their demonic guards&#8230; which seems to be an interesting idea in the making&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
